53:43.880 --> 53:45.250
U.S. Marshal!

53:47.390 --> 53:49.850
[♪]

53:57.260 --> 53:59.000
[♪]

54:04.500 --> 54:06.640
Sarah pender?

54:06.640 --> 54:09.640
I need to see your hands.

54:13.410 --> 54:15.850
[♪]

54:21.850 --> 54:22.850
All clear!

54:22.860 --> 54:25.590
Marshal,
she's not here.

54:25.590 --> 54:27.390
We're all clear.

54:29.930 --> 54:32.460
[♪]

54:32.470 --> 54:34.400
Put it on an a.P.B.,

54:34.400 --> 54:36.330
And get the photos of pender
out on the wires.

54:36.340 --> 54:38.900
Start with border control.
Alert america's most wanted.

54:38.900 --> 54:41.340
We got to get her face
out there.

54:41.340 --> 54:43.710
[♪]

54:58.560 --> 55:00.820
[♪]

55:13.740 --> 55:14.770
[gasps]

55:14.770 --> 55:16.370
Your hair.

55:16.380 --> 55:18.010
I didn't recognize you.

55:18.010 --> 55:20.310
Yeah, that's the point, mimi.
Can you pay for this stuff?

55:20.310 --> 55:22.910
It's all over
the radio and tv.

55:22.920 --> 55:24.980
They've already arrested
two people.

55:24.980 --> 55:26.950
Things aren't going
exactly as planned.

55:26.950 --> 55:27.890
I can't get involved.

55:27.890 --> 55:30.050
You already are.

55:30.960 --> 55:32.720
What do you want
from me?

55:32.730 --> 55:34.020
I need an I.D.

55:34.030 --> 55:35.460
You've got to talk to
your guy at the dmv.

55:35.460 --> 55:37.530
I'm on parole!

55:38.560 --> 55:40.330
I can get you an I.D.,

55:40.330 --> 55:42.900
But they're not cheap...
Like two grand.

55:42.900 --> 55:44.000
Well, do you have
any jewelry you could sell?

55:44.000 --> 55:45.600
Clothes? Your car?

55:45.600 --> 55:47.600
I don't care how you do it,
but you owe me.

55:47.610 --> 55:49.740
I owe you?

55:49.740 --> 55:50.870
Take me
to your house.

55:50.880 --> 55:53.480
I live with
my boyfriend!

55:53.480 --> 55:54.780
We can't.

55:54.780 --> 55:56.910
I slept on a bus
last night.

55:58.350 --> 56:00.020
No idea
who she might contact,

56:00.020 --> 56:02.420
Or where she might be going?

56:02.420 --> 56:03.990
Sugar, I'm not even sure

56:03.990 --> 56:05.660
What white girl
we're talkin' about.

56:05.660 --> 56:06.890
Hmm.

56:10.630 --> 56:12.030
They all look alike to me.

56:12.030 --> 56:13.960
I'm glad she's gone.

56:13.970 --> 56:15.400
She deserves it.

56:15.400 --> 56:18.940
She's the most beautiful,
real thing in here.

56:18.940 --> 56:21.510
She's my wife.

56:21.510 --> 56:23.110
That's funny,

56:23.110 --> 56:25.640
'cause spitler said
they were in love, too.

56:25.640 --> 56:26.640
That's bull.

56:26.650 --> 56:28.010
She hated that man.

56:28.010 --> 56:29.810
He was screwing other girls
before sarah.

56:29.820 --> 56:31.680
That's why
she picked him...

56:31.680 --> 56:34.080
But she didn't trust him.

56:35.420 --> 56:37.790
[harlan]:
She kept the used condoms?

56:37.790 --> 56:38.990
As insurance,

56:38.990 --> 56:41.690
'case spit-man got
any dumb-ass ideas.

56:41.690 --> 56:42.990
Where is she, paula?

56:43.000 --> 56:45.400
Got no idea.
She didn't tell me

56:45.400 --> 56:46.500
Who was helping her
on the outside.

56:46.500 --> 56:48.500
She didn't trust you.

56:48.500 --> 56:51.540
She was protecting me
from a-holes like you.

56:56.670 --> 57:00.110
Sarah made me believe
anything was possible.

57:00.110 --> 57:02.910
She loved me for who I am.

57:02.920 --> 57:05.680
I never had to
pretend with her.

57:07.850 --> 57:10.450
Sarah saved my life.

57:12.090 --> 57:15.630
Sarah was very popular
with the other offenders.

57:15.630 --> 57:17.930
She did good things
for a lot of them.

57:17.930 --> 57:19.560
They loved her.

57:19.570 --> 57:20.900
They'll help her now.

57:20.900 --> 57:22.570
I'm counting on it.

57:22.570 --> 57:24.700
I've been chasing fugitives
for 16 years.

57:24.700 --> 57:25.900
First thing they all do

57:25.910 --> 57:27.700
Is reach back to family
and friends.

57:27.710 --> 57:29.070
[♪]

57:29.070 --> 57:31.740
Any of these women
been released?

57:31.740 --> 57:32.880
Mimi lundt.

57:32.880 --> 57:35.080
Got out last year.

57:35.080 --> 57:37.510
[♪]

57:49.890 --> 57:52.000
