57:52.000 --> 57:53.200
Ms. Lundt?

57:54.730 --> 57:57.170
I don't know where sarah is.

57:57.170 --> 57:59.940
I didn't mention
sarah pender.

57:59.940 --> 58:01.040
You didn't have to.

58:01.040 --> 58:02.140
You're a cop.

58:02.140 --> 58:03.740
It's all over the news.

58:03.740 --> 58:05.840
So you want to protect her?

58:05.850 --> 58:07.140
Protect her?

58:07.150 --> 58:09.510
I'm scared to death of her.

58:09.520 --> 58:10.480
[♪]

58:10.480 --> 58:11.950
[sighs]

58:11.950 --> 58:13.220
You're right.

58:13.220 --> 58:15.220
We can't do anything
to jeopardize your release.

58:15.220 --> 58:18.020
No one can,
not till I get out.

58:18.020 --> 58:19.560
What are you saying?

58:19.560 --> 58:24.190
If anyone does anything
to mess up my release...

58:25.530 --> 58:29.570
I will do what I have to,
to protect myself.

58:30.770 --> 58:31.970
Help! Help! It's mimi!

58:31.970 --> 58:34.670
Guard! Guard!

58:34.670 --> 58:36.970
[mimi wheezing intensely]

58:36.980 --> 58:38.840
[hushed]:
Never forget who helped you.

58:38.840 --> 58:40.040
[choking]

58:40.050 --> 58:41.810
[harlan]: Do you think
she poisoned you?

58:41.810 --> 58:46.780
I know somebody put
something in my food or drink.

58:46.790 --> 58:49.590
I want her back in prison.

58:49.590 --> 58:51.720
[♪]

59:07.940 --> 59:10.740
[♪]

59:15.010 --> 59:17.680
[♪]

59:29.560 --> 59:30.860
Hello?

59:30.860 --> 59:32.230
Hey. It's sarah.
Don't hang up.

59:32.230 --> 59:33.960
You're the last person
I want to call right now,

59:33.970 --> 59:35.130
But I need your help.

59:35.130 --> 59:36.630
So how old
are you?

59:36.640 --> 59:39.770
Are you coming
to my birthday?

59:39.770 --> 59:41.170
Well, I'll certainly try.

59:41.170 --> 59:42.770
Her birthday's
not for a few months.

59:42.780 --> 59:45.740
I'm gonna be a princess.

59:45.740 --> 59:47.110
Go on, baby.

59:48.910 --> 59:50.780
She is really cute.

59:50.780 --> 59:52.750
And a handful.

59:52.750 --> 59:54.720
Sarah...

59:54.720 --> 59:56.750
You gave me my life back.

59:59.020 --> 01:00:00.720
I'm glad
I could help you, but--

01:00:00.730 --> 01:00:03.260
I would never go anything
to hurt you or your kids.

01:00:03.260 --> 01:00:05.000
You have to trust me.

01:00:05.000 --> 01:00:07.760
But I'm broke, farrell.

01:00:07.770 --> 01:00:10.130
I'm gonna need real money
to pull this off.

01:00:10.140 --> 01:00:12.270
I'm willing to do whatever.

01:00:14.210 --> 01:00:16.810
Well, there's this guy, bob.

01:00:16.810 --> 01:00:20.710
I know him from dancing
at the club.

01:00:21.880 --> 01:00:23.050
Okay.

01:00:23.050 --> 01:00:24.050
[harlan]: She's manson.

01:00:24.050 --> 01:00:25.980
She's gandhi.

01:00:25.990 --> 01:00:28.350
She's gay...
She's straight,

01:00:28.350 --> 01:00:31.250
She's a blonde,
she's a brunette.

01:00:31.260 --> 01:00:35.730
She's an angel,
she's the devil.

01:00:35.730 --> 01:00:37.060
She uses people,

01:00:37.060 --> 01:00:38.760
She gets them to do
what she wants,

01:00:38.760 --> 01:00:39.830
Then she discards them.

01:00:39.830 --> 01:00:41.630
We're getting hits
from the a.P.B.

01:00:41.630 --> 01:00:43.670
A gas station
in ozark, missouri.

01:00:43.670 --> 01:00:45.740
A drugstore
in kingman, arizona.

01:00:45.740 --> 01:00:48.310
A street corner
in jacksonville, florida.

01:00:48.310 --> 01:00:50.240
Let local authorities
chase those.

01:00:50.240 --> 01:00:52.780
These are women
in a 200-mile radius

01:00:52.780 --> 01:00:55.980
Who went through rockville
when pender was there,

01:00:55.980 --> 01:00:57.150
More than half of them

01:00:57.150 --> 01:00:58.780
Are strippers
and/or prostitutes.

01:00:58.780 --> 01:01:01.050
Start canvassing the streets
and clubs.

01:01:01.050 --> 01:01:03.090
Someone knows where she is.

01:01:03.090 --> 01:01:05.060
But be careful.
She's in survival mode.

01:01:05.060 --> 01:01:07.190
Got nothin' to lose.

01:01:07.190 --> 01:01:09.790
All right,
let's get to it.

01:01:12.200 --> 01:01:14.830
[knocking at door]

01:01:16.200 --> 01:01:18.100
You must be ashley.

01:01:18.100 --> 01:01:20.870
And you must be bob.

01:01:20.870 --> 01:01:22.910
It was 400, right?

01:01:22.910 --> 01:01:25.780
Hope you're not in a hurry.

01:01:37.360 --> 01:01:40.320
How long
you been married?

01:01:40.330 --> 01:01:43.160
35 years...
To life.

01:01:44.160 --> 01:01:45.400
When did you
get divorced?

01:01:45.400 --> 01:01:48.170
We're still
married, actually.

01:01:48.170 --> 01:01:50.970
He's a cop.

01:01:50.970 --> 01:01:53.100
We used to be
crazy in love,

01:01:53.110 --> 01:01:57.210
Then he just started
going psycho with jealousy.

01:01:57.210 --> 01:01:58.310
Thought I was flirting
with everyone,

01:01:58.310 --> 01:02:01.210
He hit me a few times.

01:02:01.210 --> 01:02:03.380
Son of a bitch.

01:02:04.980 --> 01:02:07.380
I really know
how to pick 'em.

01:02:09.050 --> 01:02:11.460
[cell phone rings]

01:02:14.890 --> 01:02:16.060
Excuse me.

01:02:16.060 --> 01:02:17.460
Sure.

01:02:21.730 --> 01:02:23.000
Farrell?

01:02:23.000 --> 01:02:25.240
There are cops
at the club.

01:02:25.240 --> 01:02:27.840
They must know I helped you.

01:02:27.840 --> 01:02:29.270
No, no, no.
They're just fishing.

01:02:29.270 --> 01:02:31.040
Half the girls at rockville
have stripped there.

01:02:31.040 --> 01:02:32.380
Just drive away.

01:02:32.380 --> 01:02:33.510
You know I'll never tell
anyone you helped me.

01:02:33.510 --> 01:02:34.980
You can't come back
to my place.

01:02:34.980 --> 01:02:36.510
I won't.

01:02:36.520 --> 01:02:39.120
Just take care of your girls.
I'll figure something out, okay?

01:02:39.120 --> 01:02:41.080
Good luck.

01:02:41.090 --> 01:02:42.420
I'm sorry.

01:02:44.360 --> 01:02:46.760
[♪]

01:02:52.230 --> 01:02:54.900
Hey. Everything okay?

01:02:54.900 --> 01:02:57.030
I might need a place
to lay my head tonight.

01:02:57.040 --> 01:02:59.170
Well...

01:02:59.170 --> 01:03:02.240
Consider yourself home, baby.

01:03:08.380 --> 01:03:10.180
Can I take a bath?

01:03:10.180 --> 01:03:11.980
I haven't soaked in a tub
for years.

01:03:11.980 --> 01:03:13.450
Soak away.

01:03:13.450 --> 01:03:15.850
We've got all night.

01:03:15.850 --> 01:03:18.390
Okay.

01:03:18.390 --> 01:03:21.830
[♪]

01:03:36.310 --> 01:03:39.810
I came to indianapolis
to track down sarah pender.

01:03:39.810 --> 01:03:41.510
Pender's a convicted killer

01:03:41.510 --> 01:03:44.820
Who's been on the run
for 72 hours now,

01:03:44.820 --> 01:03:47.950
And there's no telling
what she's capable of next,

01:03:47.950 --> 01:03:53.020
So if you've seen sarah pender,
call us at 1-800-crime-tv.

01:03:53.030 --> 01:03:56.090
She needs to be
back behind bars tonight.

01:04:02.530 --> 01:04:03.830
You're still
wearing clothes.

01:04:03.840 --> 01:04:05.370
And your face
is all over tv.

01:04:05.370 --> 01:04:07.300
You're sarah pender.

01:04:07.310 --> 01:04:09.270
I believed
you were in trouble.

01:04:09.270 --> 01:04:10.510
I am in trouble.

01:04:10.510 --> 01:04:11.540
-I'm not what they say I am!
-No. No.

01:04:11.540 --> 01:04:13.180
-[thump at door]
-what did you do?

01:04:13.180 --> 01:04:14.980
Were you gonna kill me?

01:04:14.980 --> 01:04:16.380
[maid]:
Turn-down service?

01:04:16.380 --> 01:04:18.010
No! We're good. Thank you.

01:04:18.020 --> 01:04:19.880
Just let me go.
You can keep your money.

01:04:19.890 --> 01:04:22.620
I don't want my money.

01:04:24.260 --> 01:04:25.560
I want you.

01:04:30.290 --> 01:04:31.530
I know I should've
called the cops

01:04:31.530 --> 01:04:32.600
Right afterwards.

01:04:32.600 --> 01:04:35.900
I should've told them
about rick.

01:04:35.900 --> 01:04:38.300
But I did more than
enough time

01:04:38.300 --> 01:04:39.440
For that one mistake,

01:04:39.440 --> 01:04:41.400
And I wasn't about
to do any more.

01:04:41.410 --> 01:04:44.110
[phone vibrating]

01:04:48.180 --> 01:04:49.310
Betty your wife?

01:04:49.310 --> 01:04:51.050
[sighing wearily]

01:04:51.050 --> 01:04:52.450
Well...

01:04:52.450 --> 01:04:55.120
What are you
gonna do now?

01:04:55.120 --> 01:04:58.090
My plans are... Fluid.

01:04:59.320 --> 01:05:01.260
Well, let me help you.

01:05:01.260 --> 01:05:03.930
I'll book the room
for another night.

01:05:03.930 --> 01:05:06.600
I can come here
after work tomorrow.

01:05:07.570 --> 01:05:10.000
And after that?

01:05:12.670 --> 01:05:15.440
If you really want
to help me,

01:05:15.440 --> 01:05:17.240
Help me get a job...

01:05:17.240 --> 01:05:19.510
A good job
that pays cash.

01:05:19.510 --> 01:05:20.680
Shouldn't you
be thinking about

01:05:20.680 --> 01:05:22.010
Trying to
leave the country?

01:05:22.010 --> 01:05:24.010
They'll be
expecting me to run.

01:05:24.020 --> 01:05:26.350
Is about the last thing
anyone expects me to do.

01:05:26.350 --> 01:05:28.350
Got any skills?

01:05:28.350 --> 01:05:30.420
Any other skills?

01:05:30.420 --> 01:05:31.590
[laughs]

01:05:31.590 --> 01:05:32.960
Accounting.

01:05:32.960 --> 01:05:34.190
Second-oldest profession.

01:05:34.190 --> 01:05:35.960
In high school, I did
the books and payroll

01:05:35.960 --> 01:05:37.390
For my father's
landscaping business.

01:05:37.400 --> 01:05:38.500
What do you do?

01:05:38.500 --> 01:05:40.530
Paper goods.

01:05:40.530 --> 01:05:43.070
Distribution.
I own hopner supplies.

01:05:43.070 --> 01:05:46.200
So that's like, what?
Napkins, cups, plates?

01:05:46.200 --> 01:05:48.340
Very good.

01:05:48.340 --> 01:05:50.040
That's cool.

01:05:51.310 --> 01:05:53.540
You really are
something else.

01:05:53.550 --> 01:05:56.180
Most women don't care
about what I do.

01:05:56.180 --> 01:05:57.650
I get it.

01:05:57.650 --> 01:05:59.380
It's not a very
sexy business.

01:05:59.380 --> 01:06:01.250
But it's made me rich.

01:06:01.250 --> 01:06:03.250
Which is sexy.

01:06:03.260 --> 01:06:04.690
You must be able
to think of something

01:06:04.690 --> 01:06:07.390
I can do
with my skills.

01:06:09.260 --> 01:06:10.490
Her name's ashley.

01:06:10.500 --> 01:06:11.960
She's my wife's cousin,

01:06:11.960 --> 01:06:13.530
But she's in
a little bit of a situation.

01:06:13.530 --> 01:06:14.660
She knows accounting.

01:06:14.670 --> 01:06:16.270
Okay, I'll start
the paperwork.

01:06:16.270 --> 01:06:19.340
Well, I'd rather
keep it off the books for now,

01:06:19.340 --> 01:06:22.410
So just pay her 10 bucks an hour
out of petty cash.

01:06:22.410 --> 01:06:24.110
I told her she could
start tomorrow.

01:06:24.110 --> 01:06:25.210
Thanks, jer.

01:06:28.180 --> 01:06:29.180
Do you trust him?

01:06:29.180 --> 01:06:31.180
Jerry?
Are you kidding me?

01:06:31.180 --> 01:06:33.280
He's been with me
for more than 10 years,

01:06:33.290 --> 01:06:35.350
He's not gonna say
anything to anyone.

01:06:35.350 --> 01:06:37.150
Okay.

01:06:37.160 --> 01:06:39.490
[producer]: Do you know
who's helping sarah?

01:06:39.490 --> 01:06:41.290
She's out free
while richard hull,

01:06:41.290 --> 01:06:42.560
Scott spitler,
and yourself

01:06:42.560 --> 01:06:43.730
