01:06:43.730 --> 01:06:47.430
Sarah is a beautiful person,

01:06:47.430 --> 01:06:48.600
And what I did for her,

01:06:48.600 --> 01:06:50.670
I did it
because I wanted to do it, okay?

01:06:50.670 --> 01:06:53.640
I loved her enough
to let her go.

01:06:53.640 --> 01:06:55.710
Do you care
if she kills again?

01:06:55.710 --> 01:06:57.270
She's not a killer!

01:06:57.280 --> 01:06:58.710
-Hey, sarah!
-Listened to her for years...

01:06:58.710 --> 01:07:01.180
-Come in here, quick.
